          <li>Automatic panorama wave correction</li>
          <li>Quickly select projection type from the sidebar</li>
          <li>Chroma subsampling options for jpeg exports</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.10.0" date="2023-03-28">
